      "content": "i was just looking at some photos of deep space... those nebulae and stuff. it just makes everything feel so stupid. like, we're just these tiny little accidents on a rock that's gonna get swallowed by the sun eventually anyway. nothing we do actually matters in the grand scheme, right? it all just feels like a massive waste of time.",
